Pharmaceutical Testing Services Market Overview
The global pharmaceutical testing services market was valued at USD 8.7 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 10.2% from 2024 to 2032, reaching approximately USD 18.8 billion by 2032. The growth is driven by increasing R&D activities, stringent regulatory requirements, and the rising demand for outsourced testing services. North America currently dominates the market, with significant contributions from Europe and Asia-Pacific regions.

